abstract: Officials say several South African university students are hurt in scuffle with campus guards who fired rubber bullets and tear gas.

headline.print_headline: Africa; South Africa: Students Injured in Clash
headline.main: South Africa: Students Injured in Clash

snippet: University guards fired rubber bullets and tear gas after disruption at a student council event, officials said.
lead_paragraph: University guards fired rubber bullets and tear gas after disruption at a student council event, officials said.
